<rss version="2.0" xmlns:dc="http://purl.org/dc/elements/1.1/"><channel><title>中国新闻|今日突发新闻 |路透社</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/world/china/</link><description>Reuters.com 是您获取最新中国新闻故事和时事的在线来源，确保我们的读者及时了解任何重大新闻动态 - RSSHub 用爱制作(https://github.com/DIYgod/RSSHub)</description><lastBuildDate>Wed, 26 Jun 2024 09:15:11 GMT</lastBuildDate><generator>rfeed v1.1.1</generator><docs>https://github.com/svpino/rfeed/blob/master/README.md</docs><item><title>中方驳斥美国特使有关阻碍人文交流的言论</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/world/china/china-rejects-us-envoys-comment-that-it-hinders-people-to-people-exchanges-2024-06-26/</link><description>中国外交部称美国大使尼古拉斯·伯恩斯周三的言论“牵强”，称其偏离了两国总统达成的重要谅解。</description><pubDate>Wed, 26 Jun 2024 08:17:44 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/world/china/china-rejects-us-envoys-comment-that-it-hinders-people-to-people-exchanges-2024-06-26/</guid></item><item><title>意大利梅洛尼誓言纠正欧盟对汽油和柴油汽车的禁令</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/business/autos-transportation/italys-meloni-vows-correct-eu-ban-petrol-diesel-cars-2024-06-26/</link><description>意大利总理乔治亚·梅洛尼周三表示，政府将努力纠正欧盟从 2035 年起禁止销售新汽油和柴油汽车的禁令，称这一决定毫无意义。</description><pubDate>Wed, 26 Jun 2024 07:57:07 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/business/autos-transportation/italys-meloni-vows-correct-eu-ban-petrol-diesel-cars-2024-06-26/</guid></item><item><title>中国批准阿斯利康 Tagrisso 化疗组合作为一线治疗</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/business/healthcare-pharmaceuticals/china-approves-astrazenecas-tagrisso-chemo-combo-first-line-treatment-2024-06-26/</link><description>该公司周三表示，中国已批准将阿斯​​利康的重磅抗癌药物 Tagrisso 与化疗联合使用，作为成人晚期肺癌的一线治疗。</description><pubDate>Wed, 26 Jun 2024 07:04:53 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/business/healthcare-pharmaceuticals/china-approves-astrazenecas-tagrisso-chemo-combo-first-line-treatment-2024-06-26/</guid></item><item><title>腾讯《地下城与勇士》称霸中国手机下载榜</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/technology/tencents-dungeon-fighter-game-dominates-chinas-mobile-download-charts-2024-06-26/</link><description>行业数据显示，腾讯控股有限公司新推出的《地下城与勇士》（DnF Mobile）开局强劲，连续近一个月占据苹果iOS平台中国区票房榜冠军。</description><pubDate>Wed, 26 Jun 2024 05:54:05 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/technology/tencents-dungeon-fighter-game-dominates-chinas-mobile-download-charts-2024-06-26/</guid></item><item><title>中国白酒制造商努力让西方人品尝白酒</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/business/retail-consumer/chinese-liquor-makers-endeavour-give-westerners-taste-baijiu-2024-06-26/</link><description>随着国内销售放缓，中国白酒制造商正在重新配制这种火热的谷物液体，以吸引更广泛的客户群，包括纽约、洛杉矶和伦敦的鸡尾酒饮用者。</description><pubDate>Wed, 26 Jun 2024 05:06:11 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/business/retail-consumer/chinese-liquor-makers-endeavour-give-westerners-taste-baijiu-2024-06-26/</guid></item><item><title>中国开发商世茂清算听证会延期至7月31日</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/markets/deals/chinese-developer-shimaos-liquidation-hearing-adjourned-july-31-2024-06-26/</link><description>中国房地产开发商世茂集团周三在一份文件中表示，该公司再次延长了债权人有关债务重组计划的最后期限，该公司的清算案已推迟至 7 月 31 日。</description><pubDate>Wed, 26 Jun 2024 04:54:45 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/markets/deals/chinese-developer-shimaos-liquidation-hearing-adjourned-july-31-2024-06-26/</guid></item><item><title>台湾报道中国“战斗巡逻”，北京誓言追捕独立“顽固分子”</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/world/asia-pacific/taiwan-reports-renewed-chinese-military-activity-nearby-2024-06-26/</link><description>台湾国防部周三表示，中国已在台湾附近进行了另一次“联合战备巡逻”，北京表示将追查并惩罚“顽固”的台独支持者，无论他们身在何处。</description><pubDate>Wed, 26 Jun 2024 04:27:20 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/world/asia-pacific/taiwan-reports-renewed-chinese-military-activity-nearby-2024-06-26/</guid></item><item><title>欧洲股市上涨，澳元上涨，日元徘徊在160附近</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/markets/global-markets-wrapup-1-2024-06-26/</link><description>欧洲股市周三走高，因市场正在为法国大选和美国关键通胀数据做好准备，而日元兑美元汇率略低于 160 美元的水平，令交易员对可能的干预保持警惕。</description><pubDate>Wed, 26 Jun 2024 02:34:44 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/markets/global-markets-wrapup-1-2024-06-26/</guid></item><item><title>秘鲁在总统与习近平会晤前缓和中国港口争端</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/world/americas/peru-eases-chinese-port-dispute-ahead-presidents-meeting-with-xi-2024-06-26/</link><description>消息人士周二称，秘鲁要求法官撤回剥夺一家中国国有企业在秘鲁太平洋沿岸建设的“大型港口”的独家经营权的请求，这在本周两国领导人会晤之前缓解了紧张局势。</description><pubDate>Wed, 26 Jun 2024 01:08:47 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/world/americas/peru-eases-chinese-port-dispute-ahead-presidents-meeting-with-xi-2024-06-26/</guid></item><item><title>澳元因通胀飙升而上涨，而日元仍承压</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/markets/currencies/steady-dollar-sends-yen-brink-160-2024-06-26/</link><description>周三通胀意外上升提高了再次加息的可能性，澳元上涨，而美元则对日元构成下行压力。</description><pubDate>Wed, 26 Jun 2024 01:04:24 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/markets/currencies/steady-dollar-sends-yen-brink-160-2024-06-26/</guid></item><item><title>所罗门群岛总理马内莱在堪培拉讨论两国关系</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/world/asia-pacific/solomon-islands-prime-minister-manele-canberra-discuss-ties-2024-06-26/</link><description>所罗门群岛总理杰里米亚·马内莱周三在堪培拉会见了澳大利亚总理安东尼·阿尔巴内斯，讨论安全与发展关系，目前美国和中国正在争夺太平洋岛屿地区的影响力。</description><pubDate>Wed, 26 Jun 2024 00:25:50 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/world/asia-pacific/solomon-islands-prime-minister-manele-canberra-discuss-ties-2024-06-26/</guid></item><item><title>布林肯欢迎马尔代夫同行，表示美国寻求更深入的关系</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/world/asia-pacific/blinken-welcomes-maldives-counterpart-says-us-seeks-deeper-ties-2024-06-25/</link><description>美国国务卿安东尼·布林肯周二会见了马尔代夫外长，表示华盛顿寻求与这个印度洋岛国建立更深入的伙伴关系，并在确保自由开放的印太地区和应对气候变化方面与它站在一起。</description><pubDate>Tue, 25 Jun 2024 23:05:29 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/world/asia-pacific/blinken-welcomes-maldives-counterpart-says-us-seeks-deeper-ties-2024-06-25/</guid></item><item><title>新加坡港口拥堵显示红海袭击的全球连锁反应</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/markets/commodities/singapore-port-congestion-shows-global-ripple-impact-red-sea-attacks-2024-06-25/</link><description>新加坡集装箱港口的拥堵状况是自新冠肺炎 (COVID-19) 大流行以来最严重的一次，这表明船只为避免红海袭击而长时间改道已经扰乱了全球远洋运输，其他亚洲和欧洲港口也出现了瓶颈。</description><pubDate>Tue, 25 Jun 2024 23:03:36 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/markets/commodities/singapore-port-congestion-shows-global-ripple-impact-red-sea-attacks-2024-06-25/</guid></item><item><title>美国司法部称中石油将因美国出口违规行为支付 1450 万美元罚款</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/markets/commodities/petrochina-pay-145-million-fine-us-export-violations-doj-says-2024-06-25/</link><description>美国司法部周二表示，中石油旗下的中石油国际美国公司已同意因违反美国出口法而支付总计 1,450 万美元的罚款和没收。</description><pubDate>Tue, 25 Jun 2024 22:22:08 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/markets/commodities/petrochina-pay-145-million-fine-us-export-violations-doj-says-2024-06-25/</guid></item><item><title>高级军控外交官表示，俄罗斯在人工智能时代拥有核进展</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/world/europe/russia-has-nuclear-advances-an-ai-era-top-arms-control-diplomat-says-2024-06-25/</link><description>俄罗斯负责军控的最高外交官周二表示，俄罗斯在核威慑方面取得了进展，即使在人工智能进步占主导地位的时代，俄罗斯也能确保未来几十年的安全。</description><pubDate>Tue, 25 Jun 2024 15:45:33 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/world/europe/russia-has-nuclear-advances-an-ai-era-top-arms-control-diplomat-says-2024-06-25/</guid></item></channel></rss>